member.summary:
计算BIAS
BIAS :(CLOSE-MA(CLOSE,N))/MA(CLOSE,N)*100;
BIASMA :MA(BIAS, M);

zhaoma/N=4,M=4

计算CCI
TYP:=(HIGH+LOW+CLOSE)/3; CCI:(TYP-MA(TYP, N))/(0.015*AVEDEV(TYP, N));
默认参数：N=14 AVEDEV 绝对平均偏差= 1/n * (求和：|xi-x均|，i=1,2,3...n) 比如说三个数，59，60，61，平均值为60 绝对平均偏差就是 1/3 * ( |59-60| + |60-60|+ |61-60|)=0.667=0.7

ENE指标

UPPER:(1+M1/100)*MA(CLOSE,N);
LOWER:(1-M2/100)* MA(CLOSE, N);
ENE:(UPPER+LOWER)/2;

计算KD
LOWV:=LLV(LOW, N);
HIGHV:=HHV(HIGH, N);
RSV:=EMA((CLOSE-LOWV)/(HIGHV-LOWV)*100,M);
K:EMA(RSV, M);
D:MA(K, M);

默认参数 N=9 M=3

计算MACD
DIF:EMA(CLOSE,SHORT)-EMA(CLOSE,LONG);
DEA:EMA(DIF,MID);
MACD:(DIF-DEA)*2,COLORSTICK;
默认 SHORT=12 LONG=26 MID=9
